00_AYBzd6XahaehJzxXDgf14XOXpGtOGFLZ0ju8BYCf5stE9A&oe=66FBDB81"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Landscape_2560_1440_Oculus1.png", "id": "1138853546573929", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001717_1138853549907262_6485199567914041408_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hRYDb2ZAm_kQ7kNvgGfI9KU&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA0Pg45mT0JrebqgFP3VYGH0s24tN7h_LCDX0Bifc6luA&oe=66FBDF7B"}, "display_name": "Windlands", "keywords": ["grapple", "parkour", "swing", "hooks", "explore"], "long_description": "A first-person grappling hook exploration game.\n\nSoar through the ruins of a fallen civilization and discover the secrets of the ancient world.\n\nIt appeals to those who want to explore the breathtaking vistas at a relaxing pace, while the challenging routes attract gamers who like to master the skill of soaring through the towering environments at top speed.\n\n{423280110561253}\n\nGameplay Features\n\n* Designed and built for Virtual Reality First.\n* Grappling Hooks Focused Movement.\n* Variety of expansive levels that reward exploration.\n* Multiple routes provide a range of optional challenges.\n* Optional Skill based Speed Runs and Time Trials\n* Goal Driven Gameplay with Easy (Hook Anything), Normal and Hard Modes.\n\n{1506211596983092}", "short_description": "A first-person grappling hook exploration game. Soar through the ruins of a fallen civilization and discover the secrets of the ancient world."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.psytecgames.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.psytecgames.com/terms/", "publisher_name": "Psytec Games Ltd", "support_website_url": "https://www.psytecgames.com/support", "website_url": "http://www.windlands.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_FEW", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id":